summary: This is a search and seizure warrant authorizing the search of Little Saint James Island in the U.S. Virgin Islands on July 24, 2019. The warrant commands law enforcement to search for and seize property related to violations of federal law, including evidence of criminal activity.

events.title: Search of Little Saint James Island
events.description: A search and seizure warrant is executed at Little Saint James Island, authorizing law enforcement to search for and seize property related to violations of federal law.

locations: Little Saint James Island, U.S. Virgin Islands
keyFacts: A federal search warrant was issued for Little Saint James Island on July 24, 2019.
The warrant authorized seizure of property related to violations of federal law.
The search was to be conducted during daytime hours (6:00 a.m. to 10:00 p.m.).
The document is a legal authorization for law enforcement to search the property.
The warrant references violations of U.S. Code, indicating a federal investigation.
